- Um...

245
00:18:51,820 --> 00:18:53,279
Was it for you?

246
00:18:53,364 --> 00:18:54,822
I don't know.

247
00:18:55,282 --> 00:18:56,658
He didn't say anything.

248
00:18:56,992 --> 00:18:58,701
How'd you know it was a he?

249
00:19:00,371 --> 00:19:01,913
You got a girl?

250
